title: Here's why Ronda Rousey is angry with Justin Bieber
text:
Melbourne: Looks like Ronda Rousey is very angry with Justin Bieber as she recently revealed that the singer dissed her at the Cannes Film Festival.

Ronda Rousey. Pic/ Santa Banta 
The 28-year-old UFC women's bantamweight champion said that the 'Baby' hit-maker was really rude to her at the festival when she asked him to get a picture clicked with her younger sister, reports News.com.au.
Rousey added when she went to the 21-year-old singer and asked for a picture, he said that he has already taken a billion pictures today and walked off.
She added that her 16-year-old sister was on the verge of crying at the moment and said that she is no longer a Belieber.
